<h1 style="margin:0 0 8px;color:#1e293b;font-size:24px;font-weight:700;">
    You have been invited!
</h1>
<p style="margin:0 0 16px;color:#64748b;font-size:15px;line-height:1.6;">
    <strong style="color:#1e293b;">@Model.InvitedByName</strong> has invited you
    to join <strong style="color:#1e293b;">@Model.GymName</strong> on FitCore.
</p>
<p style="margin:0 0 32px;color:#64748b;font-size:15px;line-height:1.6;">
    Create your account to get started — track workouts,
    book classes and manage your fitness journey.
</p>
<table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">
    <tr>
        <td style="border-radius:8px;background:#22c55e;">
            <a href="@Model.RegisterUrl"
               style="display:inline-block;padding:14px 32px;color:#ffffff;
                font-size:15px;font-weight:600;text-decoration:none;">
                Accept Invitation
            </a>
        </td>
    </tr>
</table>
<p style="margin:32px 0 0;color:#64748b;font-size:13px;line-height:1.6;">
    This invitation expires in <strong>7 days</strong>.<br>
    If you were not expecting this invitation you can safely ignore this email.
</p>